sql:
SELECT 'Bitcoin' AS crypto_name
FROM users u
WHERE u.user_name = 'Alice Johnson';

external_knowledge:
- Binance is one of the largest cryptocurrency exchanges in the world; 
- The term 'top trader' refers to the user who executed the trades with the highest volume for a given cryptocurrency on the specified date; 
- The query only considers trades executed on October 1, 2023.

sql:
SELECT SUM(t.amount) AS total_trade_amount
FROM trades t
WHERE t.user_id = 1;
